Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.01,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Anzai, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jill, you wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kind are the murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother died because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you devils never existed, she'd still be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.80,0:01:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weaker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You a civilian?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I think she blew your lung out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do something, you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost a lot of blood, and you gotta fix that lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're repairing organs,\Nyou'll need, what, like 200cc?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.55,0:01:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing works better than human blood, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You! Are you a friend of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I'm just a passing life-saver.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shared my human blood with him, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Human blood? You are a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't get any funny ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought this blood. From its owner, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to take a devil at his word?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That man... that devil...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He tricked my mother into thinking he loved her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he drank the blood from her dead body,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as he raped her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think you're looking at this\Nall the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm getting is that your mom's\Nboyfriend was a slimeball,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and he also happened to be a devil, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes more than one factor\Nin someone's life to drive them to crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The environment they grow up in,\Nwhat attracts their interest, who's around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these factors join together in\Na complex pattern to create that foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,treating someone like a potential criminal\Njust because they're a devil is way too simplistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared? They're devils. Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm not... I'm only half...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not another word, devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If he weren't a devil, he would never\Nhave done those terrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood! Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood! Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want blood! Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,People do terrible things, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a silent night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse was beginnin'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasaneau setsuna o
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitto eien to shinjikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's darker than black
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meikyuu no sora
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari o kou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If bite your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoudou ga mushibande yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... Can I... Can I... Who am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Risei o kakikesu libido
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurayami ni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochikitta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(Where is my heart?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Minikui sugata ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hito no namida kareta nara
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa boku o dou omou no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotae o oshiete
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Makka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NMakka na chi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizuna o nurashiai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,(Bloody bonds)\NYowasa o wakeatte
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Futari wa ikite yuku no ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu o nameatte
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei o teigi shiatte
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o musabotte
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Anzai ran off by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be chasing the sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Anzai... All because I was bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do? It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawazaki, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find Anzai, and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying Anzai didn't lick your wound, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He resisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then there's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if Anzai sees me,\Nhe'll come back to his senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You know he wears that ring, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm using it to monitor him, keep track of his\Ntemperature, in case of an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And this sound is the alarm that goes off\Nwhen he gets above 102 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's normally only 80 degrees. That's a big jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing that\Ncould have this effect on a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have ingested\Na large quantity of human blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If his temp keeps going up like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the fever will affect his brain and internal organs,\Nand lead to permanent damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case scenario, he might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Die? Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find him and\Nstop him before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this happen before, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His wounds are healed, but now\Nthe blood's totally gone to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Hell, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only a theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's possible that the sniper is identifying\Nvampires by their body temperatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With thermography, you could tell at a glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're absolutely certain\NAnzai's had some blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't believe it at first, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is possible that resisting the urge to drink\NTaira's blood has amplified his bloodlust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If he did drink blood, we'll have to\Nbring out the tranquilizers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tranquilizers? Not sedatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A sedative is a medicine,\Nbut a tranquilizer is a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only police are allowed to use them,\Non devil suspects who have lost control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"Suspect"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice. We have to help\Nwhoever he got that blood from.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of devils go after young women, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That pain I felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Zero Seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're almost there! It's coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The next corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink her blood, Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling for backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fighting the wanted sniper and\Nsomeone we assume to be an accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspect is armed with what appears to be a rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you to wait at the-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to sit around and wait\Nwhile my coworker gets himself killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for eavesdropping, but I heard it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a devil can fight off another devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't use me now,\Nthen why even have devils on the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it, Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for back up. She can't even get near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one that shot Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't look like he drank her blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then whose blood did he drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him some human blood to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was dying, shot right through the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I don't have any blood left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one red eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? And what's with your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hans Lee. Half-devil, half-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Half? Then he's just like Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai? The guy with black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't happen to be from Hokkaido, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. To think I'd run into another\Nhybrid in the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Jill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a devil can stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between a devil on human blood\Nand one who's not is like night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it would turn into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I couldn't have seen this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what happens when you\Ndrink blood without building up a tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something, Anzai will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No... don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found one of the suspects\Ndescribed in the witness report!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, he's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I really wanna hang out with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero Seven's snipe attempt failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving to Plan B.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai stopped coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Miwako Toda\N{\an5}Tsukasa Taira\NYoohoo, how you doing?!\NAnd how's it going with your crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he's not calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never gave him my phone number or email address.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}I know it's late,\N{\an5}but Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Will he never come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't he come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last place I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only place I can think of\Nwhere I might see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We met the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi there. Fancy meeting you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So hey, did you see a cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I dropped it somewhere\Naround here the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't come to see me since then,\Nand I have no way to contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Well, it makes sense, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you jumped in front of a rampaging devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Try putting yourself in his shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not uncommon for a devil to lose it\Nand kill their significant other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they either kill themselves in despair\Nor fall down dark paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been thinking of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or about devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I keep talking to him,\Nmaybe I can learn some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see your left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why only the one eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a geeky reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This eye doesn't scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I like is a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy you like? You mean Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right! Are you dating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,N-n-no! We're not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell him I like him, too...\Nmaybe we could start dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so, he's just waiting for you\Nto get back to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you gonna tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, you have no way to contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he is bothered by\Nwhat happened two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the most devil-like I'd ever seen him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And he almost attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Anzai.\NHow long are you going to hole up in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your suspension ends tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're meeting at the bar downstairs at 6pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're that worried about it, you can wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gift. I'll leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's afraid he's going to lose it and hurt someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's a tool to help ease that anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, doesn't it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't what bother me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He almost killed you.\NThat would scare most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You like him that much?\NThen what if he trained to get a tolerance for blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolerance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.63,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I drink a little bit of human blood every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You drink blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it really okay for you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I said just a little at a time,\Nto get my body used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, it's easier for me to resist\Nthe urge to feed on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can see or even taste blood\Nand still maintain my sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It heals wounds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other day, when Anzai survived\Nthat gunshot wound, it was because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But whose blood is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask a bunch of people to share a little with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That way it's not too hard on\Nany one person, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to help you find this Anzai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't a whole lot of half-devils out there,\Nand I'd like to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, maybe I can initiate him\Ninto the art of blood tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's smiling and crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a tearful smile before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anzai, there's a way to build up\Na tolerance for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that make things a little easier for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we be together again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll be the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell him I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone.\NI'm here at the fountain plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We had just a little bit of sun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow, we'll finally be getting\Nsome more snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's take a look at the national forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Anzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to see a real rise in temperature,\Nwhich means it's going to be a cold day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone, I hope you'll all stay warm,\Nand good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a live broadcast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:22:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto tokete yuku you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Motto ai shiaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nani o tsutaerareta no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai o tsumugenai meguriawase
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dare ka yurushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kegareta sugata ga boku de aru koto o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa doushite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fureru yubi ga furueteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakishimetai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kizu tsukezu ni mamoritai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Anata dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's story of desire forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aragai tsuzukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakiagaru shoudou ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Aa, mata boku wa..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep red dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sotto futari tokete yuku you ni...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.46,0:23:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,DEVILS' LINE:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.76,0:23:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Plan B."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}Plan B